Package: scratchrobin
Version: 1.0.0
Section: database
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libwxgtk3.2-1 | libwxgtk3.0-gtk3-0v5, libsecret-1-0
Recommends: libpq5, libmysqlclient21 | libmariadb3
Suggests: firebird3.0-utils
Maintainer: Dalton Calford <dcalford@stacktrace.ca>
Description: Database administration tool for ScratchBird
 ScratchRobin is a lightweight, ScratchBird-native database
 administration tool inspired by FlameRobin. It provides a
 comprehensive GUI for managing ScratchBird databases with
 support for PostgreSQL, MySQL, and Firebird through optional
 backend adapters.
 .
 Features include:
  - Visual table designer
  - ERD diagramming with auto-layout
  - SQL editor with syntax highlighting
  - Reverse/forward engineering
  - User and role management
  - Backup and restore
